textDesc.derivation:
this document is labeled "original" because the XML-TEI
               markup of it's contents have not made any alterations to the original
               content;

list.item:
English translations are defined in relation to their Mixtec equivalents in
                     the following location:
                        //text[@xml:lang='mix']/body/div/p/spanGrp[@type='translation']/span[@xml:lang='en']
                     the value of //span[@target] is the pointer to the Mixtec translation
                        equivalentwhere a preceding sibling is:
                        //text[@xml:lang='mix']/body/div/p/seg

Spanish translations are defined in relation to their Mixtec equivalents in
                     the following location:
                        //text[@xml:lang='mix']/body/div/p/spanGrp[@type='translation']/span[@xml:lang='es']
                     the value of //span[@target] is the pointer to the Mixtec translation
                        equivalent where a preceding sibling is:
                        //text[@xml:lang='mix']/body/div/p/seg
